软件包 darks.codec

类摘要
Codec Codec interface.
CodecConfig Codec configuration object.
CodecParameter Codec parameter.
Decoder Decoder is the interface to decode message object in codec.
Encoder Encoder is the interface to encode message object in codec.
ObjectCoder ObjectCoder is the main API class for developer.
 

枚举摘要
CodecConfig.CacheType Cache type
CodecConfig.EndianType Endian type
CodecConfig.TotalLengthType Total length type
